@page "/chinh-sach-bao-mat"
@model PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Chinh sach bao mat";
    ViewData["Description"] = "Chinh sach bao mat thong tin khach hang khi mua dau dua CoPuree tren website.";
}

<section class="policy-page">
    <p class="eyebrow">CoPuree policy</p>
    <h1>Chinh sach bao mat</h1>
    <p>CoPuree chi thu thap thong tin can thiet de xu ly don hang, giao hang, cham soc khach hang va cai thien trai nghiem mua sam truc tiep tren website.</p>
    <h2>Thong tin thu thap</h2>
    <p>Ho ten, so dien thoai, email neu co, dia chi giao hang, ghi chu don hang va lich su giao dich.</p>
    <h2>Cach su dung</h2>
    <p>Thong tin duoc dung de xac nhan don, giao hang, ho tro doi tra, gui thong bao lien quan den don hang va cac uu dai CoPuree khi khach hang dong y.</p>
    <h2>Bao ve du lieu</h2>
    <p>Du lieu don hang can duoc luu tren hosting co mat khau manh, HTTPS va sao luu dinh ky. Khi ket noi cong thanh toan, khong luu thong tin the ngan hang tren website.</p>
</section>
